text: Lev Martyushev (, 1880 - 20 December 1937) was a Russian fencer. He competed in three events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1880 births Category:1937 deaths Category:Russian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Russia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
